#(.env)
VITE_API_URL=https://backend-production-1234.up.railway.app/api

VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY="place-your-api-key"

── Email (SMTP) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
Set these to enable real email dispatch. Uses Gmail App Password.
Leave blank to run in DRY_RUN mode (emails logged to console only).
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=
SMTP_PASSWORD=
EMAIL_FROM=noreply@rashtra-solapur.gov.in

Dept contact emails (used for routing notifications)
DEPT_EMAIL_ENGINEERING=engineering@solapur-mc.gov.in
DEPT_EMAIL_TRAFFIC=traffic@solapur-mc.gov.in
DEPT_EMAIL_WARD=ward@solapur-mc.gov.in
DEPT_EMAIL_WATER=water@solapur-mc.gov.in
